name: BEAUTY WILL SAVE THE WORLD V2

metadata.name: Blue and Yellow
metadata.description:
In a world where there is chaos, it is important to support each other. 70% of the cost of the work will be transferred to a fund to help Ukrainian residents.

With this work, I would like to express my condolences to all the people who have to experience fear and horror while experiencing this war.

There should be no wars in the world. But sadly, I couldn't stop the war. I can only continue to live and create beauty.
